    "body": "This is actually a feature of Chromium, and unfortunately it doesn't provide any option for this:\nhttps://bugs.chromium.org/p/chromium/issues/detail?id=244955\nhttps://bugs.chromium.org/p/chromium/issues/detail?id=353430\n\nI suggest creating an issue at Chromium's issues list to request an option to exclude shadow DOM form searching. I'm closing this since it is a hard-coded feature of Chromium, and we are not able to fix it alone on Electron's side.\n"
